  </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══ FINAL CTA ════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section class="relative overflow-hidden py-20 lg:py-28" style="background:#0A0A0A;">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none" style="background:radial-gradient(ellipse 50% 70% at 75% 50%,rgba(232,180,176,0.06) 0%,transparent 70%);"/>
  <div class="container-x relative z-10 text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto">
    <p class="text-[9px] uppercase tracking-[0.26em] font-bold mb-5" style="color:rgba(232,180,176,0.5);">Your results next</p>
    <h2 class="font-display text-3xl lg:text-5xl text-white leading-tight tracking-[-0.02em] mb-6 text-balance">
      See your ROI before<br/><em class="font-medium" style="color:#E8B4B0;">committing to anything.</em>
    </h2>
    <p class="text-[14px] leading-relaxed mb-10 max-w-lg mx-auto" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.38);">
      In 60 minutes we map your workflows, quantify the exact time and money on the table, and hand you a prioritised automation roadmap. No pitch. No commitment.
    </p>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 justify-center">
